      • mergeEditingContext

        public void mergeEditingContext(SnomedEditingContext dirtyEditingContext,
                                SnomedEditingContext newEditingContext)
                         throws MergeFailedException
        Description copied from interface: ICDOEditingContextMerger
        Merges all the changes made on the dirtyEditingContext argument to a brand new editing context specified as the newEditingContext argument.
        Parameters:
        dirtyEditingContext - the dirty editing context where the changes have been made. Cannot be null.
        newEditingContext - the brand new editing context instance. Cannot be null. Cannot be dirty.
        Throws:
        MergeFailedException - if the merge failed due to stale references.
